Brazil Tax Agency May Probe Employee Stock Options, Valor Says

-- B y   T e l m a   M a r o t t o
-- 
2011-03-16T12:17:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/brazil-tax-agency-may-probe-employee-stock-options-valor-says.html
  Brazil ’s federal tax agency wants
to investigate publicly traded companies that award stock
options to employees for tax-avoidance purposes,  Valor Economico 
reported, without saying where it got the information.  The agency considers such operations as “abusive tax
planning,” the Sao Paulo-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
